title: 9 Albums From Early 90s
description:
Some great albums out of a handful of good stuff released in the early 90's. I hope you like them. Canadapal, your Grant Hart's record is posted here. Time to retire that poor old tape! Nova Mob was Grant Hart's solo record titled "Last Days Of Pompeii".


Divinyls - Divinyls (1990)

Dream Command - Fire on the Moon [1990]

Energy Orchard - Energy Orchard [1990]

Nova Mob - Last Days Of Pompeii [1991]

'O'Rang - Herd of Instinct [1994]

Schnell Fenster - The Sound Of Trees [1990]

The Caretaker Race - Hangover Square [1990]

Thomas Lang - The Lost Letter Z [1992]

To The Fountain - The Horse Won't Lie Down [1990]
